### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@shortCode = abc123

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Crear URL Corta
POST {{baseUrl}}/shorten
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://www.example.com/very/long/url"
}

### Obtener URL Original
GET {{baseUrl}}/shorten/{{shortCode}}

### Actualizar URL
PUT {{baseUrl}}/shorten/{{shortCode}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://www.updated-url.com"
}

### Eliminar URL
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/shorten/{{shortCode}}

### Obtener Estadísticas
GET {{baseUrl}}/shorten/{{shortCode}}/stats

### Probar validación - URL inválida
POST {{baseUrl}}/shorten
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "invalid-url"
}

### Probar validación - URL faltante
POST {{baseUrl}}/shorten
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Probar 404 - Short code inexistente
GET {{baseUrl}}/shorten/noexiste